{"article_id":"V2nLkU1xI4WwSv5l","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"This week the Supreme Court unblocked most aspects of President Trump 's executive order","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"limiting entry into the United States ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"signaling","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that the restrictions are likely to be upheld .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"That makes sense ,","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"because the reasons","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"that two federal appeals court offered","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"for upholding injunctions against Trump 's order","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"are unpersuasive .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"But the fact","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"that Trump 's policy is legal","depth":4},{"id":11,"text":"does not make it smart .","depth":3},{"id":12,"text":"The original version of Trump 's order was issued in great haste","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"a week after he took office ,","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"and it showed .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"The 90-day ban on entry by citizens of seven Muslim-majority countries","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"( Iran , Iraq , Libya , Somalia , Sudan , Syria , and Yemen )","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"applied to current visa holders ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"including people","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"working and studying in the United States ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and legal permanent residents ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who were barred from returning home","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"after traveling abroad .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Adding to the confusion ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the travel ban took effect immediately ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"stranding residents and visitors in mid-trip","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"without notice .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"The result was dismay and disorder at airports around the world","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"as officials , travelers , and lawyers grappled with the new policy .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"After the order was blocked by the courts ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"Trump issued a revised version on March 6 ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"clarifying","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that the travel ban did not apply to legal permanent residents ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"who have a right to due process","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"when the government tries to prevent their re-entry ,","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"or to current visa holders ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"whose hosts may have standing","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to sue .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Notably , the order","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"issued by the Supreme Court on Monday","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"says","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"while the case is pending","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"the travel ban should not be enforced against visa applicants or would-be refugees with a `` bona fide relationship '' to Americans , such as relatives , students","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"accepted by U.S. universities ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"employees","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"hired by U.S. companies , or lecturers","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"booked","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to speak here .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"The revised order also eliminated Iraq from the list of targeted countries","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"and excised language","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"favoring religious minorities","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"from the section","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"imposing a 120-day moratorium on admission of refugees .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Critics cited that preference as evidence","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that the order was motivated by anti-Muslim bias .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The U.S. Court of Appeals for the 4th Circuit nevertheless concluded","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that the March 6 order `` in context drips with religious intolerance , animus , and discrimination . ''","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"The context","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that the court deemed relevant","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"consisted mostly of statements","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"made by Trump or his surrogates before and after the election ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"including his support for `` a total and complete shutdown of Muslims","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"entering the United States . ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"But that is not the policy","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Trump actually tried to implement ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and relying on his campaign comments","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to conclude","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"that his executive order is a `` Muslim ban '' in disguise","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"leads to strange results .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"The plaintiffs conceded , for example ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"if Hillary Clinton had been elected president","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"and issued exactly the same executive order ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"it `` could be constitutional . ''","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"The U.S. Court of Appeals for the 9th Circuit relied on a different rationale","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"when it upheld an injunction against Trump 's order ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"he exceeded his statutory authority","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"because he did not make an evidence-based determination","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"that admitting the people","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"he wants to exclude","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"would be `` detrimental to the interests of the United States . ''","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"But that was really just another way","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"of saying","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that Trump 's policy ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"which is supposedly aimed at protecting Americans from terrorists ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"is half-baked and empirically unsound .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"That much is true .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Since 1975 , no terrorist from any of the countries","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"covered by the travel ban","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"has killed anyone in the United States ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"and the odds","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"of being killed by a refugee","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"are infinitesimal .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"In any case , it has never been clear why a travel ban was necessary","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"for Trump to deliver the `` extreme vetting ''","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"he promised .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"Even the `` total and complete '' Muslim ban","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"he originally proposed","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"was supposed to last","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"only as long as it took to `` figure out what is going on , ''","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"which","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"according to his executive orders","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"means three months .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Trump has been president for more than five months .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"By his own account , he could have made any necessary improvements in traveler screening by now .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"His failure","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"to do so","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"provides further evidence","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"that his policy is just for show .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":221,"left":122,"right":220,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":119,"right":121,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":112,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":4,"right":117,"relation":